                                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                                        <h3 class="f-20 text-green">Andre Chiang</h3>
                                        <div>Country Manager/Director of Gen Partners</div>
                                        <p class="m-t-10">Common Ground - is definitely not your run-of-the-mill work-space. This is the real deal. While work may seem like a drag for many, Common Ground is quite the contrary bringing out the best in you with it's great atmosphere, well decked interiors and professional team that resonates with so much warmth you'll feel right at home. Actually, Common Ground is home to me and my team. In my opinion, you'll NEVER find a team of people so dedicated to making your work-space work for you - and the coffee is great too. The ironic truth is that there is nothing 'common' about these grounds. They are in fact a gem of a find.</p>
