                                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                                        <h3 class="f-20 text-green">Francesca Chia</h3>
                                        <div>Co-Founder of GoGet</div>
                                        <p class="m-t-10">Many traditional businesses have perception that working in a co-working space is expensive and not worth it. But I genuinely save money by working in CG. After taking into consideration rental for a 2 year lease, in a location that is not central so that its cheaper, having to fit out the office internally, pay for all utilities, cleaning services, pantry items, maintenance and repairs, furniture etc, you will see that the cost per month shoots up a lot on top of your base rental rate. On top of that, our company can remain asset light, have admin for the office all taken care off, plus we get value from gym subscriptions, community events and partnerships. The value we get is more than just the rental fee, CG goes out of their way to help our team grow as a business. Their team is very personable and professional.</p>
                                    </div>
