                                        <h3 class="f-20 text-green">Niney Chong</h3>
                                        <div>Founder of Image Empowerment</div>
                                        <p class="m-t-10">Common Ground was a life saver for me! I had to relocate to KL with a 2 weeks notice to pursue a startup ChatBot Malaysia. CG made it seamless for both my partner and I we can focus on our startup while all the nitty gritty of settling up a new office taken care by CG and its amazing team. I even get to pursue my passion a community organization on women empowerment called Mompreneur Asia with the support of CG. Community driven that’s what CG is about for me. Instead of dreading to go to office the environment and 5 star set up by CG for its members is now EXCITING!! I’m a raving fan! My circle of friends are excited to have meetings with me at “My Office”. It’s modern, hip and warm what more can you ask for?? Especially love working with my CG KEN TTDI Community Managers.</p>
